Package elevator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Elevator
    Represents an Elevator Object.
    ElevatorDriver
    This class is the Driver class for the Elevator simulation.
    ElevatorPerson
    This class represents a person that wants to use the elevator.
    ElevatorStack
    This class represents the space available in the Elevator.
    MyStack
    Custom Stack class that will be used to hold ElevatorPerson Objects.
    ReadFile
    This class reads the input data for the elevator simulation.
    WriteFile
    This class writes the data to an output file for the elevator simulation.
